#########
# INPUT #
#########

The input file should be formated as the following:

x y z
v0_count
v0_x v0_y v0_z
.
.
.
v0_x v0_y v0_z
p_x p_y p_z
.
.
.
p_x p_y p_z
p_x p_y p_z1
.
.
.
p_x p_y p_z1
.
.
.

To see a example run: make examples
